name: deep_codegen_cross_set_count_after_conditional_mutation
section: codegen-cross-feature
args: p:Bool a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: conditional set mutation must produce expected runtime count.
law: (= (with [s (set {a})] (do (if {p} (conj! s {b}) (disj! s {a})) (count s))) (if {p} (count (set {a} {b})) 0))
